text:
It has been the butt of the joke in the Internet mostly bc of the lower efficacy rates but the difference is quite understandable when looking at how where/when the phase 3 ran: <https://www.nbcnews.com/health/health-news/how-effective-johnson-johnson-vaccine-what-know-n1259652> Safety wise I think it has gone quite smoothly.

I def appreciate the single trip (it’s an hour away). Plus I have a trip late April till mid May so I don’t have to worry about when I could schedule the 2nd one.
